msgid "A bee who has been recognized as a trusted contributor. These bees have demonstrated ability in relation to a specific part of the BeeWare project over a period of time. This could be on a technical level (JavaScript, Python, Objective-C expertise; GTK+, macOS knowledge), or on another level (community management, code review). Apiarists may also have the commit bit for the project where their expertise is recognized."
